      <div class="p-8 lg:p-10">
        <span class="text-white font-medium">‚è§ Literature review</span><h2
          class="lg:text-6xl text-balance py-3 tracking-wide text-white">
          Discussions on critical texts
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-4 bg-zinc-800 gap-px lg:items-start"
        x-data="{ testimonialActive: 2 }">
        <div
          class="p-8 lg:pl-10 shrink-0 gap-2 h-full flex items-center bg-black">
          <button
            @click.prevent="testimonialActive = 1"
            class="font-bold rounded-full focus:outline-none ize-12 focus:ring-2 size-12 ring-black ring-offset-black shrink-0"
            :class="{'h-12 w-12 opacity-70  ': testimonialActive != 1, 'opacity-100  text-black': testimonialActive == 1 }"
            ><img
              class="size-12 rounded-full"
              src="https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1311131959612104706/IW-LA7Cj_400x400.jpg"
              alt="#_"
            /></button
          ><button
            @click.prevent="testimonialActive = 2"
            class="font-bold rounded-full focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 size-12 ring-black ring-offset-black shrink-0"
            :class="{'h-12 w-12 opacity-70  ': testimonialActive != 2, 'opacity-100  ': testimonialActive == 2 }"
            ><img
              class="inline-block size-12 rounded-full"
              src="https://alfred.lexingtonthemes.com/avatar2.png"
              alt="#_"
            /></button
          ><button
            @click.prevent="testimonialActive = 3"
            class="font-bold rounded-full focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 size-12 ring-black ring-offset-black shrink-0"
            :class="{'h-12 w-12 opacity-70  ': testimonialActive != 3, 'opacity-100  text-black': testimonialActive == 3 }"
            ><img
              class="inline-block size-12 rounded-full"
              src="https://alfred.lexingtonthemes.com/avatar3.png"
              alt="#_"
            /></button
          >
        </div>
        <div
          class="p-8 lg:px-10 flex flex-col bg-black items-start gap-6 lg:col-span-3">
          <div class="flex ">
            <div
              x-show="testimonialActive == 1"
              style="display: none;">
              <p class="text-white text-sm font-medium">Mike Andreuzza</p>
              <a
                href="#_"
                class="text-xs text-zinc-400"
                >Founder of Lexington Themes</a
              >
            </div><div x-show="testimonialActive == 2">
              <p class="text-white text-sm font-medium">Juan Ymedio</p><a
                href="#_"
                class="text-xs text-zinc-400"
                >Founder of TodoEntero.</a
              >
            </div><div
              x-show="testimonialActive == 3"
              style="display: none;">
              <p class="text-white text-sm font-medium">Miguel Durain</p><a
                href="#_"
                class="text-xs text-zinc-400">
                Founder of Pouch</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-zinc-400 text-base text-balance">
            <div
              x-show.immediate="testimonialActive === 1"
              style="display: none;">
              <p
                x-show.transition="testimonialActive == 1"
                style="display: none;">
                StudioMaX is a true rarity, effortlessly bridging the realms of
                design and coding. His designs are masterfully polished,
                striking a perfect balance between being on trend and remaining
                distincltly original.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div x-show.immediate="testimonialActive === 2">
              <p x-show.transition="testimonialActive == 2">
                StudioMaX has a great eye for design and he is an absolute
                pleasure to work with. I definitely plan on working with him on
                future projects of mine. I wholeheartedly recommend him to
                anyone seeking standout, quality work.
              </p>
            </div><div
              x-show.immediate="testimonialActive === 3"
              style="display: none;">
              <p
                x-show.transition="testimonialActive == 3"
                style="display: none;">
                StudioMaX is a rare breed of designer & dev that understands
                business needs. He leveraged his previous experience to build
                out a few landings very quickly for Versoly.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
